```r
##80-20 split
set.seed(1)
sample<-sample.int(nrow(house), floor(.80*nrow(house)), replace = F)
train<-house[sample, ]
test<-house[-sample, ]
head(train)
```

<!-- rnb-source-end -->

<!-- rnb-chunk-end -->


<!-- rnb-text-begin -->



<!-- rnb-text-end -->


<!-- rnb-chunk-begin -->


<!-- rnb-source-begin eyJkYXRhIjoiYGBgclxucHJvcC50YWJsZSh0YWJsZSh0cmFpbiR2YWx1ZSkpXG5gYGAifQ== -->

```r
prop.table(table(train$value))
```

<!-- rnb-source-end -->

<!-- rnb-chunk-end -->


<!-- rnb-text-begin -->




<!-- rnb-text-end -->


<!-- rnb-chunk-begin -->


<!-- rnb-source-begin eyJkYXRhIjoiYGBgclxuZnVsbF9tb2RlbDwtZ2xtKHZhbHVlIH4gYmF0aHJvb21zK2JlZHJvb21zK3NxZnRfbGl2aW5nK2Zsb29ycyt3YXRlcmZyb250K3ZpZXcrZ3JhZGUrc3FmdF9saXZpbmcxNSthZ2UsIFxuICAgICAgICAgICAgICAgIGZhbWlseT1cImJpbm9taWFsXCIsIGRhdGE9dHJhaW4pXG5zdW1tYXJ5KGZ1bGxfbW9kZWwpXG5gYGAifQ== -->

```r
full_model<-glm(value ~ bathrooms+bedrooms+sqft_living+floors+waterfront+view+grade+sqft_living15+age, 
                family="binomial", data=train)
summary(full_model)
```

<!-- rnb-source-end -->

<!-- rnb-chunk-end -->


<!-- rnb-text-begin -->



<!-- rnb-text-end -->


<!-- rnb-chunk-begin -->


<!-- rnb-source-begin  -->

```r
library(ROCR)
# Get predictions based on test holdout set
preds <- predict(full_model, newdata=test, type='response')
rates <- prediction(preds, test$value)
roc_result <- performance(rates, measure = 'tpr', x.measure = 'fpr')
plot(roc_result, title="The ROC curve")+
lines(x = c(0,1), y = c(0, 1), col="red")

```

<!-- rnb-source-end -->

<!-- rnb-chunk-end -->

cf <- table(test$value, preds>0.5)
cf
